Bernanke Reiterates That China’s Yuan Significantly Undervalued

-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z
-- 
2011-10-04T16:13:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/bernanke-reiterates-that-china-s-yuan-significantly-undervalued.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said  China ’s currency is significantly undervalued and
its exchange-rate policies are impeding a global economic
recovery.  He said China’s yuan policy is “certainly a negative” in
response to questions today from the Joint Economic Committee of
Congress.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
